The Twitter streets are ablaze with the news that popular Xitsonga soapie which aired on SABC2, Giyani Land of Blood is coming to an end this month. Sunday Sun published that the much-loved telenovela drawing to a close, seasoned actor Fumani Shilubana told the paper it was worth having a Xitsonga series in mainstream television. “Through this show we’re making it okay, Charles Baloyi and I fought hard for our language to be in the mainstream,” he said.